      "content": "That makes sense, but I'm getting some pushback from our engineering team. They're saying that focusing on these \"existential risks\" is a bit of a distraction and that most of it is just speculative sci-fi. Can you weigh in on whether these risks are actually considered a serious, evidence-based concern by the scientific community, or if they're mostly just theoretical?",
